sql_query.sql: SELECT "user_ips".* FROM "user_ips" WHERE "user_ips"."user_id" = $1 ORDER BY "user_ips"."user_id" ASC LIMIT $2

SELECT "statuses"."id", "statuses"."updated_at" FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "accounts" ON "accounts"."id" = "statuses"."account_id" WHERE "statuses"."visibility" = $1 AND "accounts"."suspended_at" IS NULL AND "accounts"."silenced_at" IS NULL AND (statuses.reply = FALSE OR statuses.in_reply_to_account_id = statuses.account_id) AND "statuses"."reblog_of_id" IS NULL AND 1=1 AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC LIMIT $2
